did.unittitle: Yale objects collection

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The collection consists of objects and memorabilia related to Yale including artwork, apparel, silver and porcelain place settings, building hardware, engraving plates, and fraternity insignia.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 45 (YRG 45), Yale objects and memorabilia.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: These objects are available for research.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale Objects Collection (RU 104). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged by object number.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The collection consists of objects and memorabilia related to Yale including artwork, apparel, silver and porcelain place settings, building hardware, engraving plates, and fraternity insignia.
